import React from 'react'
import {Provider} from 'react-redux'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import App from './App'

const Root = ({store}) => (
    <Provider store={store}>
        <Router>
            <Route path="/" component={App} />
        </Router>
    </Provider>
)

export default Root
